### Ascend API — Social Media Tracker
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Log social media usage
POST {{baseUrl}}/social-tracker
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "INSTAGRAM",
  "minutes": 45,
  "loggedDate": "2025-06-20"
}

###

### Log TikTok usage
POST {{baseUrl}}/social-tracker
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "TIKTOK",
  "minutes": 30,
  "loggedDate": "2025-06-20"
}

###

### Get social usage history (last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/social-tracker?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete a log entry
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/social-tracker/LOG_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
